room_title: Escape room "C'thulhu Awakens" by Sly Fox Escapes in Colorado Springs
room_address: 5360 N Academy Blvd. Ste 160 Colorado Springs, CO 80918
room_description: You should not be reading this. And I certainly should not be dragging you into the disaster which I have unleashed on the world! We have returned with an ancient item that should have remained buried by the depths of the sea. Now the evil which was once trapped inside is about to be released into our world. If you are brave enough, perhaps you can stop it. If not, eldritch monsters may walk the earth again.
